import React, { Component } from "react"; import CoLinkName from './Components/CoLinkName' import "./Nav.scss" class Nav extends Component { constructor() { super(); this.state = { linkCoName: [], } } componentDidMount() { fetch('http://localhost:3000/data/LinkCoData.json', { method: 'GET' }) .then(res => res.json()) .then(res => { this.setState({ linkCoName: res }); }); } render() { console.log(this.state.linkCoName) return (
    {/*
  • Nike
  • Join US
  • 조던 이미지
  • Converse
  • 회원가입 / 로그인
  • 고객센터
  • 장바구니 아이콘
  • 위치
    • */}
) } } export default Nav;
